## SPRINT P — MİNİMUM EVENT SET (P0)

Her oturumda bu olayların app'te tanımlı ve pipeline'da olduğunu doğrula:

`app_open` · `session_start` · `session_end` · `exercise_started` · `exercise_completed` · `phrase_started` · `phrase_completed` · `phrase_skipped` · `phrase_repeated` · `premium_view` · `premium_start` · `streak_day` · `daily_mission_completed`

**Kod:** `app/src/main/java/<package>/domain/model/AnalyticsEvent.kt` — `.factory/project.json` paketine göre  
**Pipeline:** `AnalyticsRepository` → Room (local) + Firebase (remote)

